The Vital Point for Death (46)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par It is impossible for white to save the two white stones that have been engulfed by black.
\par
\par The point of this problem is to consider how to sacrifice them efficiently and lead black into a dead shape.
\par }
